pa-jail (0.9.3-1+xenial1) xenial; urgency=medium

  [ Eddie Kohler ]
  * Copy stdin's terminal setup to ptymaster.

  [ Nikhil Benesch ]
  * pa-jail: prevent truncated output
  * pa-jail: fix sanitized relative paths

  [ Eddie Kohler ]
  * Include /dev/tty in the jail; make pty the controlling terminal.
  * Use poll() instead of select().
  * Use signalfd.
  * Pass TERM environment variable along.
  * Pass stdin, stdout, stderr along to the child if not tty.
  * Jailed program declares self foreground process group.
  * A fix for when stdout is redirected.
  * Set the tty to raw mode even if it's only on stderr.
  * If -i is given, forward stdout and stderr over the pty.
  * If forwarding to a file because of -i, turn off output processing.
  * Improve help.
  * Add LICENSE (GPLv2).
  * Markderp

  [ Nikhil Benesch ]
  * Update copyright file for official LICENSE info

 -- Nikhil Benesch <nikhil.benesch@gmail.com> Mon, 05 Sep 2016 21:00:31 -0700

